MIZNER HOA
Venues to accommodate all celebrations.
Venues to accommodate all celebrations.
Row Backgrounds
Birthdays, Anniversaries, Reunions and more.
Mizner Country Club holds a tradition of creating unique celebrations that cater to each client’s style, sensibility, and whim. Mizner’s impeccable amenities provide a gorgeous backdrop while our experienced team of culinary and banquet professionals provide excellent service from start to finish.
Row Backgrounds
Spectacular event facilities and gorgeous settings.
The culinary team offers a distinguished selection of delectable cuisine that exquisitely caters to even the most discriminating palette. Each event is uniquely designed, and we are devoted to ensuring that your celebration will hold magical memories for years to come.
Row Backgrounds
Book your Event Now in our Newly Renovated Space.
Breathtaking areas with expansive views both indoors and outdoors. Don’t miss out on your spot. New available spaces to book today!
Multipurpose Room with Built-in Surround Sound and Drop-down Projection Screen
Recreational room and Mizner Kids for Kids Parties
Outdoor concert with bar area, cocktails and hors d’ oeuvres or food stations
BBQ and Pool Parties
learn more

Contact us today to book your next event!
From corporate events to intimate gatherings and private affairs, our professionals will turn your dreams into unbelievable and memorable experiences.
